    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "@mjaggard my understanding is that <code>@PostConstruct</code> is not used to inject your dependencies appropriately, to make sure they are <code>final</code>, etc; it is used as an annotation for a utility that should be called <i>exactly once</i> even if the object is constructed multiple times by the IoC container. Not that I know how this would happen in the container, but it apparently can happen (see accepted answer)."
  } ],
