      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Just be careful, if you have circular dependencies, it is possible that your AutoWired&#39;s AutoWired dependencies will still be null at PostConstruct time: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/64649202/32453\">stackoverflow.com/a/64649202/32453</a>"
