  "title" : "Why use @PostConstruct?",
  "body" : "<p>In a managed bean, <code>@PostConstruct</code> is called after the regular Java object constructor.</p>\n\n<p>Why would I use <code>@PostConstruct</code> to initialize by bean, instead of the regular constructor itself?</p>\n"
}